commit.message:
Completely revise dbskkd-cdb.c

* Use `<sysexits.h>` exit code instead of `diesys()`
* Revise indentation and C code formatting with `clang-format`
* Remove `VERBOSE_MSG` flag
Update examples.md: remove tabs from inetd example
.travis.yml: explicitly set CC from the env

Change .travis.yml to enable multiple compilers

* Travis CI exports `gcc` or `clang` into `$CC`
* Move all C compilation flags to COMPAT from CC
Add Travis CI status to README.md
